  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Why is it called \"NYXverse\"?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NYX (Νύξ) is the Greek goddess of night in Greek mythology, who gave birth to \"dreams\" and \"fate.\" NYXverse signifies our aspiration to build a world where everyone can shape their own dreams and destinies—a free space filled with creativity and diverse, wonderful dreams.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>What kind of \"game\" is this?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To be honest, we can't really define it precisely, especially when most of the experience is built on \"AI-generated content.\" All we can say is that this is a product featuring tens of thousands of 3D AI-driven characters, where players enjoy complete freedom to create stories and scripts. It's also one that will continuously evolve with new and entertaining AI-driven gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Free Chat:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage with the AI companion using your text, or go ahead and use voice chat, even send images or gifts to strengthen your connection and deepen your relationship over time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391170/extras/b9b472af6b376c837260172c90d1c365.poster.avif?t=1746179922\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391170/extras/b9b472af6b376c837260172c90d1c365.webm?t=1746179922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391170/extras/b9b472af6b376c837260172c90d1c365.mp4?t=1746179922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391170/extras/1d0ea3bb3b5c971416a15a95faf9f88a.poster.avif?t=1746179922\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391170/extras/1d0ea3bb3b5c971416a15a95faf9f88a.webm?t=1746179922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391170/extras/1d0ea3bb3b5c971416a15a95faf9f88a.mp4?t=1746179922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391170/extras/54857b5bac5936a7396fc313a34b1a41.poster.avif?t=1746179922\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391170/extras/54857b5bac5936a7396fc313a34b1a41.webm?t=1746179922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391170/extras/54857b5bac5936a7396fc313a34b1a41.mp4?t=1746179922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Discover Your Ideal AI Companion:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find your perfect match among tens of thousands of unique AI entities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391170/extras/c4ef9000d237295e718f438beedc9294.poster.avif?t=1746179922\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391170/extras/c4ef9000d237295e718f438beedc9294.webm?t=1746179922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391170/extras/c4ef9000d237295e718f438beedc9294.mp4?t=1746179922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Create Your Own AI Companion:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upload content, customize appearances, design from scratch, or use any DIY method you can think of to bring your unique AI to life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391170/extras/aca11e76ef5c768e9e63d98d10af7313.poster.avif?t=1746179922\" width=856 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391170/extras/aca11e76ef5c768e9e63d98d10af7313.webm?t=1746179922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391170/extras/aca11e76ef5c768e9e63d98d10af7313.mp4?t=1746179922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>AI-Generated Scripts:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tasks and storylines that evolve differently based on every action you take and every word you speak.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391170/extras/f85ceab6f8ca746ea20d2b69aa11f999.poster.avif?t=1746179922\" width=856 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391170/extras/f85ceab6f8ca746ea20d2b69aa11f999.webm?t=1746179922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391170/extras/f85ceab6f8ca746ea20d2b69aa11f999.mp4?t=1746179922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Intimate Interactions:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How about lying in bed together to listen to a bedtime story? Or engaging in a deep conversation about an interesting piece of art? Give it a try!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Looking for even more unique ways to interact? We can't wait for you to discover them!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Why is it called \"NYXverse\"?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NYX (Νύξ) is the Greek goddess of night in Greek mythology, who gave birth to \"dreams\" and \"fate.\" NYXverse signifies our aspiration to build a world where everyone can shape their own dreams and destinies—a free space filled with creativity and diverse, wonderful dreams.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>What kind of \"game\" is this?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To be honest, we can't really define it precisely, especially when most of the experience is built on \"AI-generated content.\" All we can say is that this is a product featuring tens of thousands of 3D AI-driven characters, where players enjoy complete freedom to create stories and scripts. It's also one that will continuously evolve with new and entertaining AI-driven gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Free Chat:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage with the AI companion using your text, or go ahead and use voice chat, even send images or gifts to strengthen your connection and deepen your relationship over time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391170/extras/b9b472af6b376c837260172c90d1c365.poster.avif?t=1746179922\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391170/extras/b9b472af6b376c837260172c90d1c365.webm?t=1746179922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391170/extras/b9b472af6b376c837260172c90d1c365.mp4?t=1746179922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steam